  <eBankitHtml><![CDATA[<p>Because buying a home is a very important step, the MORTGAGE LOAN from ebankIT helps in making a decision.<br /><br /></p>
<p><strong>Minimum amount:</strong> 10.000,00 EUR<br /> <strong>Maximum amount:</strong> 100.000,00 EUR<br /> <strong>Period:</strong> 50 years</p>
<p><br /><br /></p>
<p><strong>Goal:</strong><br /> The acquisition, construction and works in permanent housing.<br /><br /> <strong>Period:</strong><br /> Up to 40 years, with the limit of 75 years of age.<br /><br /> <strong>Bonus Credit for People with Disabilities:</strong><br /> This type of financing is intended for the acquisition, construction or realization of works in permanent private housing and allows disabled citizens (under the law 64/2014 and with incapacity equal to or greater than 60%), to benefit from a subsidized rate.</p>]]></eBankitHtml>
